.Dd July 26, 2013
.Dt MKIMG 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm mkimg
.Nd "utility to make a disk image"
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl b Ar bootcode
.Op Fl o Ar outfile
.Op Fl p Ar partition
.Op Fl s Ar scheme
.Op Fl z
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility creates a disk image from the raw partition contents and using the
partitioning scheme specified.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr makefs 8
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
utility appeared in
.Fx 10.0
